component_description: Detection results for Goal Reminder Prompt

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Header Text
elements.description: Dark gray text 'Get a daily reminder to meet your goal' centered at the top portion of the white screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the header text, with only a very slight excess in horizontal padding; remains readable and central.

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Mascot
elements.description: Green cartoon owl character holding a yellow bell, positioned in the upper middle section of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box generally fits the full owl and bell graphic. Slight excess padding on the left and bottom. Main subject is mostly well-contained.

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Speech Bubble
elements.description: White speech bubble containing the text 'Just in case you forget!' positioned to the right of the green owl character
elements.explanation: Bounding box almost perfectly matches the speech bubble position and size, with only minor excess outside the lower and right edges.

component_description: Detection results for Notification Permission Card

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Container
elements.description: White rounded rectangle card with notification permission information, occupying the middle section of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the visible white notification card; very minor excess padding horizontally but otherwise well fit.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > App Icon
elements.description: Small square green icon showing owl eyes, positioned at the left side within the notification text area
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly encompasses the green square app icon with minimal background; accurate.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Notification Text
elements.description: Gray text stating 'The website "duolingo.com" would like to send you notifications in Notification Center.' centered in the upper portion of the white card
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly includes the notification text block and is well-centered and fit; minor excess on the bottom margin.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Additional Info
elements.description: Small gray text 'Notifications can be changed in Safari Website preferences.' positioned at the bottom of the notification text section
elements.explanation: Box includes the additional info text but is slightly too wide and tall, extending more left and right than needed.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Block Button
elements.description: Light gray rectangular button with 'BLOCK' text, positioned at the bottom left corner of the notification card
elements.explanation: Bounding box aligns well with 'BLOCK' button including the full area and a small margin; well matched.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Allow Button
elements.description: Blue rectangular button with white 'ALLOW' text, positioned at the bottom right corner of the notification card
elements.explanation: Box is tightly fit around 'ALLOW' button, tracking its edges; highly accurate.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Arrow Indicator
elements.description: Blue upward-pointing arrow below the notification permission card
elements.explanation: Small arrow is almost perfectly surrounded by the bounding box with negligible extra space.

elements.label: Continue Button > Button
elements.description: Large green rectangular button with rounded corners containing white 'CONTINUE' text, spanning the width of the lower portion of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the button's position and size, with only a slight extra vertical padding at the bottom corners.
